headlines.description: — Giannis Antetokounmpo scored 37 points, Damian Lillard had nine of his 28 in the final minute and the Milwaukee Bucks returned to the NBA Cup semifinals in Las Vegas by beating the Orlando Magic 114-109 on Tuesday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Bucks beat Magic 114-109 to return to the NBA Cup semifinals in Las Vegas

events.name: Dallas Mavericks at Oklahoma City Thunder

headlines.description: — Shai Gilgeous-Alexander scored 39 points, and the Oklahoma City Thunder beat the Dallas Mavericks 118-104 on Tuesday night in an NBA Cup quarterfinal.
headlines.shortLinkText: Gilgeous-Alexander scores 39 as Thunder beat Mavericks 118-104, advance to NBA Cup semifinals
